# xiao-citizen host-compiled test binaries (built locally via make).
# Wildcard pattern matches any new test_* / emit_* binaries the Makefile
# adds without requiring a .gitignore edit each time. Source files
# (.cpp / .h / .json / .md) are explicitly re-included.
xiao-citizen/tests/test_*
xiao-citizen/tests/emit_*
!xiao-citizen/tests/*.cpp
!xiao-citizen/tests/*.h
!xiao-citizen/tests/*.json
!xiao-citizen/tests/*.md
